                     <interp inst="t18310407-47-verdict275" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 35.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy by the Prosecutor, having a wife and family.</p>
